{"data":[{"name":"78:1","price":"¿Sobre qué se preguntan unos a otros?","arabic":"عَمَّ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5673,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:2","price":"Sobre la gran noticia [el Mensaje del Islam]","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلنَّبَإِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5674,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:3","price":"acerca de la cual discrepan.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي هُمۡ فِيهِ مُخۡتَلِفُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5675,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:4","price":"Pero no es lo que piensan, ya verán [por desmentirla].","arabic":"كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5676,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:5","price":"Indudablemente no es lo que piensan; ya verán.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5677,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:6","price":"¿Acaso no hice de la tierra un lecho,","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ مِهَٰدٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5678,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:7","price":"de las montañas estacas,","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَوۡتَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5679,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:8","price":"los cree en parejas [hombre y mujer],","arabic":"وَخَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5680,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:9","price":"hice que el sueño sea descanso,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا نَوۡمَكُمۡ سُبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5681,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:10","price":"que la noche lo cubra,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلَّيۡلَ لِبَاسٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5682,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:11","price":"que el día sea para procurar el sustento,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلنَّهَارَ مَعَاشٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5683,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:12","price":"construí sobre ustedes siete cielos firmes,","arabic":"وَبَنَيۡنَا فَوۡقَكُمۡ سَبۡعٗا شِدَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5684,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"Ver Corán 23:86 y su comentario.","lang":"es"},{"name":"78:13","price":"puse una lámpara resplandeciente [el Sol],","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا سِرَاجٗا وَهَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5685,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:14","price":"e hice descender de las nubes agua abundante","arabic":"وَأَنزَلۡنَا مِنَ ٱلۡمُعۡصِرَٰتِ مَآءٗ ثَجَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5686,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:15","price":"para que broten semillas y plantas","arabic":"لِّنُخۡرِجَ بِهِۦ حَبّٗا وَنَبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5687,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:16","price":"y florezcan jardines frondosos?","arabic":"وَجَنَّٰتٍ أَلۡفَافًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5688,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:17","price":"El Día del Juicio Final ya está determinado.","arabic":"إِنَّ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ كَانَ مِيقَٰتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5689,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:18","price":"Ese día, se soplará la trompeta y ustedes se presentarán en grupos.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يُنفَخُ فِي ٱلصُّورِ فَتَأۡتُونَ أَفۡوَاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5690,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:19","price":"El cielo será abierto, transformándose en un portal.","arabic":"وَفُتِحَتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتۡ أَبۡوَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5691,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:20","price":"Las montañas desaparecerán como si hubieran sido un espejismo.","arabic":"وَسُيِّرَتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ فَكَانَتۡ سَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5692,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:21","price":"El Infierno estará al acecho,","arabic":"إِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ كَانَتۡ مِرۡصَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5693,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:22","price":"será la morada de los transgresores","arabic":"لِّلطَّٰغِينَ مَـَٔابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5694,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:23","price":"que permanecerán en él eternamente.","arabic":"لَّٰبِثِينَ فِيهَآ أَحۡقَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5695,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:24","price":"Allí no podrán sentir frescor ni saciar su sed.","arabic":"لَّا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا بَرۡدٗا وَلَا شَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5696,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:25","price":"Solo beberán un líquido hirviente y nauseabundo,","arabic":"إِلَّا حَمِيمٗا وَغَسَّاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5697,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:26","price":"como castigo justo por lo que hicieron [en la vida mundanal].","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ وِفَاقًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5698,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:27","price":"Ellos no esperaban tener que rendir cuentas,","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ لَا يَرۡجُونَ حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5699,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:28","price":"y por eso desmintieron abiertamente Mi Mensaje,","arabic":"وَكَذَّبُواْ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا كِذَّابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5700,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:29","price":"pero Yo lo registré todo en un libro.","arabic":"وَكُلَّ شَيۡءٍ أَحۡصَيۡنَٰهُ كِتَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5701,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:30","price":"[Se les dirá a los desmentidores:] \"Sufran las consecuencias, no haré sino aumentarles el castigo\".","arabic":"فَذُوقُواْ فَلَن نَّزِيدَكُمۡ إِلَّا عَذَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5702,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:31","price":"En cambio, los piadosos obtendrán la bienaventuranza","arabic":"إِنَّ لِلۡمُتَّقِينَ مَفَازًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5703,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"El Paraíso. ","lang":"es"},{"name":"78:32","price":"donde habrá huertos y vides,","arabic":"حَدَآئِقَ وَأَعۡنَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5704,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:33","price":"compañeras de eterna juventud,","arabic":"وَكَوَاعِبَ أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5705,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:34","price":"y copas desbordantes.","arabic":"وَكَأۡسٗا دِهَاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5706,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:35","price":"Allí no oirán banalidades ni falsedades.","arabic":"لَّا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا كِذَّٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5707,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:36","price":"Esta es la recompensa de tu Señor, que concederá generosamente.","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ مِّن رَّبِّكَ عَطَآءً حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5708,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:37","price":"El Señor de los cielos, de la Tierra y de lo que hay entre ellos, el Compasivo. Nadie puede hablar ante Él excepto con Su permiso.","arabic":"رَّبِّ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا بَيۡنَهُمَا ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِۖ لَا يَمۡلِكُونَ مِنۡهُ خِطَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5709,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:38","price":"El día en que el Espíritu junto con los demás ángeles se pongan en fila, nadie hablará, salvo aquel a quien el Compasivo se lo permita, y solo podrá decir la verdad.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلرُّوحُ وَٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ صَفّٗاۖ لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ إِلَّا مَنۡ أَذِنَ لَهُ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5710,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"el Espíritu: El ángel Gabriel.","lang":"es"},{"name":"78:39","price":"Ese es el día en que se establecerá total justicia. Quien quiera, entonces, que busque refugio en Su Señor.","arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلۡحَقُّۖ فَمَن شَآءَ ٱتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِۦ مَـَٔابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5711,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"78:40","price":"Les he advertido de este castigo inminente. Ese día cada ser humano ha de contemplar sus obras, y entonces dirá quien haya desmentido el Mensaje: \"¡Ojalá fuera polvo [para no ser juzgado]!\"","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنذَرۡنَٰكُمۡ عَذَابٗا قَرِيبٗا يَوۡمَ يَنظُرُ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مَا قَدَّمَتۡ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُولُ ٱلۡكَافِرُ يَٰلَيۡتَنِي كُنتُ تُرَٰبَۢا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5712,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"}],"chapter":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba","Chapter An-Naba","Naba","Surah Naba","Chapter Naba","An Naba","Surah An Naba","Chapter An Naba","Surah 78","Chapter 78","The Tidings","النبأ"]}